*ARTIST ANNOUNCEMENT*

Super excited to announce our next performer Dan the Man Mulqueen! @danmulqueen Dan has been at the forefront of the Handpan scene for years as a performer and teacher. If you haven't had the chance to learn from Dan before, you don't want to miss this! His unique performances incorporate electronics while keeping the Handpan at the center of his compositions for a truly amazing live set. 

"Determined to push the limits of music revolving around this instrument, Dan's playing style is both beautifully melodic and intensely percussive. His stylistic approach invites the listener to experience elements of multiple genres of music all housed in one easily digestible format."

A thing we love to do here is to give iconic scales new unexpected colors, yet to keep their distinctive flavour unaltered.
This handpan is an example of this: we made it with/for the master @danmulqueen , who beautifully played it in this video. The top is a mutant version of the legendary G Akebono scale in its natural pentatonic configuration. But it’s when combined with the bottom shell that this handpan becomes a C harmonic minor scale, bringing the player to very different scenarios from the ones you can create with the top shell. Because of that we like to call it “Spicybono”.

(Eb) (F) G/ (Ab) (B) C D Eb (F) G Ab (B) C D Eb (F) G Ab  IMPORTANT: all of our recordings are made in purity and without the addition of post-production effects such as reverb, etc., in order to offer the most truthful experience possible through headphones or with good monitor speakers.

『Tokyo Handpan Festival 2023』 八ヶ岳に世界のトップハンドパンプレイヤーが集結！ハンドパンの魅力と極上のワールドミュージックを味わえる2日間！ヨーロッパで人気の楽器ハンドパンとは？！？初の野外フェスティバルでハンドパンを体感しよう！前売りチケット、バスツアー好評発売中！
⁡
𝘿𝙖𝙣 𝙈𝙪𝙡𝙦𝙪𝙚𝙚𝙣 (𝙐𝙣𝙞𝙩𝙚𝙙 𝙎𝙩𝙖𝙩𝙚𝙨)
⁡
卓越したスキルと見るものを魅了するビートセンスとメロディライン。ハンドパンの演奏のみとは思えないほどの世界観を表現するダン・マルクイーンが満を持して来日決定！！
エレクトロニックミュージックとハンドパンを融合させたハイブリッドセットも今回の大目玉。
⁡
世界中を単独でツアーし、コロラド州のレッドロックス・アンフィシアターでShpongleとの共演をはじめ、著名なアーティストとのコラボレーションで世界的に幅位広い活躍をみせるダン・マルクイーンのミュージックはハンドパンを初めて聴く人から熱心なハンドパンファンまで幅広い層に響くことでしょう！
⁡
—
⁡
Dan Mulqueen is a versatile musician from New Jersey, known for his mastery of the handpan.Determined to push the limits of music revolving around this instrument, Dan's playing style is both beautifully melodic and intensely percussive. His stylistic approach invites the listener to experience elements of multiple genres of music all housed in one easily digestible format. While keeping the handpan as the centerpiece of his compositions, Dan's recordings also feature instruments such as upright bass, piano, electronic beats, guest vocals and more.
⁡
